node.accessibility_caption: Photo by AFTER I GOT HIGH in Boston, Massachusetts. May be an image of text that says 'AFTER GOT HIGH post #258 After I got high, I was in the garage with my guy friends and one disappeared We searched everywhere only for him to come running back, soaked head to toe. Turns out he got thirsty so instead of asking us for a water bottle from the case he went and drank from our neighbors hose.'.

node.text: We are back!! If you sent in this story, DM me to receive your prize. Make sure to send in your funniest stories each week for a chance to win!

node.text:
That's one way of keeping your car from smelling😂
